    "Table 9 illustrates the results of the ablation study and the process of obtaining a high-quality model.",
    "From our experiment, we conclude that the DWT is effective for feature extraction and that the SVM is more efficient than the Softmax algorithm for classification.",
    "Removing either the DWT or the SVM from the PolynetDWTCADx system results in a significant decrease in performance, thereby supporting the use of both DWT and SVM in the system.",
    "The analysis of the accuracy of the models indicates that the model that incorporates the integrated CNN (DEV-22) + DWT + SVM is the best model.",
    "The most effective model, DEV-22 + DWT + SVM, provides a comprehensive explanation of the classification process on the numerous classes that made up the CKHK-22 dataset through its confusion matrix and ROC curve."
